results.title: Ambiancé
results.overview: Space and time is intertwined into a surreal dream-like journey beyond places and is an abstract nonlinear narrative summary of artist Anders Weberg's time spent with the moving image.

results.title: Anita
results.overview: The story of the former beauty queen and singer, Anita Bryant, who later in life gained notoriety by campaigning in the 1970s to repeal laws that prohibited discrimination on the basis of sexual orientation.

results.title: A Man's World
results.overview: The story of boxer Emile Griffith, who took the life of fellow fighter Benny Paret in the ring during a live televised broadcast in 1962.

results.title: Nosferatu
results.overview: A 'remix' of 1922's "Nosferatu," utilizing green screen to insert new actors into the original film's environments.

results.title: The Fortress
results.overview: A group of refugees hidden aboard a container ship discover their passage to safety is not what it seems

results.title: Codename: Housewife
results.overview: An overworked and underappreciated housewife finds herself recruited by an international security force for the purposes of rescuing a group of recently kidnapped world-famous rock stars from a crazy supervillain.

results.title: Friend of the World
results.overview: After a catastrophic war, an eccentric general guides a filmmaker through a ravaged bunker.

results.title: Benedetta
results.overview: The story of Sister Benedetta Carlini, a 15th century nun who was hailed as a visionary but later accused of fabricated miracles, homosexuality and other charges, and imprisoned for 35 years.

results.title: Sons of the Neon Night
results.overview: A detective goes against the successor to a drug-trafficking crime syndicate, who aspires for a society free of drugs by orchestrating anarchy in Hong Kong.

results.title: The Swordsman
results.overview: The story of swordsmen in Joseon who were confronted with the chaos brought about by the Ming-Qing transition.

results.title: The Outlaw Johnny Black
results.overview: Hell bent on avenging the death of his father, Johnny Black vows to gun down Brett Clayton and becomes a wanted man in the process while posing as a preacher in a small mining town that's been taken over by a notorious Land Baron.

results.title: Rebecca
results.overview: The story follows a newly married young woman who, upon arriving at her husband’s imposing family estate on a bleak English coast, finds herself battling the shadow of his deceased first wife, the mysterious Rebecca, whose legacy continues to haunt the house.

results.title: Alone
results.overview: A recently widowed traveler is kidnapped by a cold blooded killer, only to escape into the wilderness where she is forced to battle against the elements as her pursuer closes in on her.

results.title: Boss Level
results.overview: A retired special forces officer is trapped in a never-ending time loop on the day of his death.

results.title: Horse Julius And Big Horse Racing
results.overview: Spin-off series "Three heroes" about the horse Julius

results.title: Superintelligence
results.overview: Carol Peters' life is turned upside down when she is selected for observation by the world's first superintelligence - a form of artificial intelligence that may or may not take over the world.

results.title: Prisoners of the Ghostland
results.overview: The film centers on notorious criminal Hero who is sent to rescue an abducted girl who has disappeared into a dark supernatural universe. They must break the evil curse that binds them and escape the mysterious revenants that rule the Ghostland, an East-meets-West vortex of beauty and violence.
